ly%20questioned%20the%2077-year-old%20former%20president's%20mental%20fitness%20and%20warned%20another%20Trump%20presidency%20would%20bring%20%26quot%3Bchaos%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20efforts%20appeared%20to%20do%20little%20to%20damage%20his%20standing%20among%20Republicans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20margin%20of%20victory%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20but%20it%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20significant%2C%20with%20major%20US%20networks%20calling%20the%20race%20within%20seconds%20of%20the%20polls%20closing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%2C%20a%20popular%20governor%20of%20South%20Carolina%20in%20the%202010s%20and%20the%20only%20woman%20to%20have%20entered%20the%20Republican%20contest%2C%20was%20looking%20to%20outperform%20expectations%20in%20her%20own%20backyard%20and%20ride%20into%20Super%20Tuesday%20with%20wind%20her%20sails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20was%20never%20able%20to%20compete%20in%20a%20battleground%20that%20preferred%20Trump's%20brand%20of%20right-wing%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20first%26quot%3B%20populism%20and%20personal%20grievance%20over%20the%20four%20indictments%20and%20multiple%20civil%20lawsuits%20he%20faces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20had%20already%20won%20Iowa%20by%2030%20points%20and%20New%20Hampshire%20by%2010%2C%20while%20a%20dispute%20in%20Nevada%20led%20to%20the%20real%20estate%20tycoon%20running%20unopposed%20in%20the%20official%20contest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20margin%20of%20Trump's%20victory%20was%20always%20the%20main%20question%20in%20South%20Carolina%2C%20with%20analysts%20arguing%20that%20Haley%20managing%20to%20whittle%20the%20gap%20to%2015%20points%20or%20less%20would%20have%20counted%20as%20a%20good%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20aides%20have%20been%20clear%20however%20that%20they%20want%20to%20see%20off%20Haley%20long%20before%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%20July%20--%20and%20are%20expecting%20the%20party%20to%20coalesce%20around%20the%20front-runner%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20of%20his%20criminal%20trials%20on%20March%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Chaos'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20made%20clear%20Saturday%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20beyond%20Haley%20to%20a%20likely%20November%20contest%20against%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20ahead%20of%20voting%20booths%20closing%20to%20the%20Conservative%20Political%20Action%20Committee%20conference%20--%20a%20must-stop%20for%20Republican%20politicians%20--%20Trump%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20time%20bashing%20Biden%2C%20not%20Haley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20--%20a%20traditional%20conservative%20who%20espouses%20limited%20government%20and%20a%20muscular%20foreign%20policy%20--%20has%20argued%20that%20a%20Trump%20presidency%20would%20be%20mired%20in%20scandal%20from%20day%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2052-year-old%20former%20UN%20ambassador%20underscored%20the%20point%20Saturday%20by%20describing%20as%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting%26quot%3B%20comments%20Trump%20had%20made%20to%20Black%20conservatives%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENodding%20to%20his%20multiple%20indictments%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BBlack%20people%20like%20me%20because%20they%20have%20been%20hurt%20so%20badly%20and%20discriminated%20against%2C%20and%20they%20actually%20viewed%20me%20as%20I'm%20being%20discriminated%20against.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20has%20also%20blasted%20Trump's%20reaction%20to%20the%20death%20of%20Russian%20dissident%20Alexei%20Navalny%20--%20he%20avoided%20criticizing%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20--%20and%20his%20threat%20to%20encourage%20Moscow%20to%20attack%20NATO%20nations%20not%20meeting%20their%20financial%20obligations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20central%20argument%20--%20that%20polling%20shows%20her%20performing%20better%20than%20Trump%20in%20hypothetical%20matchups%20with%20Biden%20--%20may%20have%20fallen%20on%20deaf%20ears%20but%20she%20has%20vowed%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20race%20through%20Super%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA