l%20major%20party%20nominees%2C%20including%20Sen.%20Mitt%20Romney%2C%20have%20lost%20either%20their%20home%20state%2C%20their%20current%20state%2C%20or%20both.%20Sen.%20George%20McGovern%20of%20South%20Dakota%20stands%20alone%20in%20the%20modern%20era.%20Amid%20a%20historic%201972%20thumping%2C%20McGovern%20carried%20just%20Washington%20DC%20and%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20our%20purposes%2C%20we're%20just%20interested%20in%20presidential%20primary%20home-state%20defeats.%20The%20Washington%20Post%20compiled%20a%20list%20of%20such%20failures%20since%201980%2C%20pointing%20out%20just%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2020%2F02%2F28%2Fif-you-dont-win-your-own-state-primary-youre-probably-not-going-be-president%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevastating%20such%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20to%20the%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20future%20Haley%20may%20find%20after%20the%20presidential%20trail.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGeorge%20H.W.%20Bush%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22George%20H.W%20Bush%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8e0cf90413ab8e1d67b6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20CIA%20Director%20George%20H.W.%20Bush%20speaks%20during%20his%201980%20GOP%20presidential%20campaign.%3Cp%3EAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%3A%201980%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContext%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Bush%20had%20compiled%20a%20lengthy%20resume.%20He%20had%20already%20served%20two%20terms%20in%20Congress%2C%20ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20under%20President%20Richard%20Nixon%2C%20led%20the%20Republican%20Party%2C%20and%20been%20CIA%20Director%20under%20President%20Gerald%20Ford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20president%20began%20the%201980%20primary%20and%20caucus%20season%20with%20a%20shocking%20victory%20in%20Iowa%2C%20narrowly%20edging%20former%20California%20Gov.%20Ronald%20Reagan%2C%20who%20had%20his%20teeth%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20as%20a%20sports%20broadcaster%20in%20the%20state.%20Bush's%20momentum%20didn't%20last%20long.%20Reagan%20started%20rattling%20off%20wins%20and%20accruing%20delegates%20across%20the%20South%20and%20Midwest.%20A%20New%20York%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1980%2F05%2F04%2Farchives%2Freagan-heads-for-narrow-victory-over-bush-in-texas-primary-vote.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn't%20overly%20harsh%20on%20Bush's%20loss%20in%20the%20state%20his%20son%20George%20W.%20would%20one%20day%20lead%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20he%20performed%20well%20in%20the%20Houston%20area%20he%20represented%20in%20Congress.%20(Bush%20also%20won%20his%20actual%20birth%20state%20of%20Massachusetts%20and%20Connecticut%2C%20where%20he%20grew%20up%2C%20during%20the%201980%20cycle.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%20less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20the%20Texas%20contest%2C%20Bush%20was%20out%20of%20the%20race.%20His%20eventual%20consolation%20prize%20was%20the%20vice%20presidency.%20He%20remains%20the%20most%20recent%20vice%20president%20to%20immediately%20replace%20the%20president%20they%20served%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJohn%20Anderson%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20B.%20Anderson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8e62f6080194819f9d0c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20John%20Anderson%20of%20Illinois%20pauses%20during%20a%20news%20conference%20amid%20his%201980%20presidential%20campaign%20that%20began%20as%20a%20bid%20for%20the%20GOP%20nomination%20before%20he%20pivoted%20to%20an%20independent%20campaign.%3Cp%3EIra%20Schwarz%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%3A%201980%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C