eavenly%20Hideaway.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jennifer%20Tucker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20church%20served%20as%20more%20than%20a%20place%20of%20worship.%20It%20was%20a%20communal%20space%20where%20the%20women%20of%20Bartlett's%20past%20gathered%20each%20Wednesday%20for%20a%20quilting%20circle%20and%20strategized%20how%20best%20to%20help%20their%20neighbors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETucker%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20women%20voted%20on%20a%20secretary%2C%20who%20was%20charged%20with%20keeping%20track%20of%20all%20their%20good%20deeds%20in%20a%20notebook.%20That%20notebook%20is%20now%20displayed%20inside%20the%20rental%20for%20guests%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20quilting%20circle%2C%20they%20would%20say%20who%20was%20sick%20in%20the%20community%2C%20how%20many%20cards%20they%20wrote%2C%20who%20they%20cooked%20for%20that%20week%2C%20who%20they%20visited%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20never%20forgot%20anybody%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20they%20always%20had%20time%20to%20raise%20an%20extra%2050%20cents%20to%20make%20sure%20there%20was%20food%20in%20the%20pantry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETucker%20purchased%20the%20church%20in%20October%202020%20and%20finished%20renovations%20in%20May%202021.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bartlett%20church%20in%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8dc0390413ab8e1d678ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovation%20process%20took%20seven%20months.%3Cp%3EErik%20Fossum%2FFossum%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20purchasing%20the%20church%20in%20October%202020%2C%20Tucker%20and%20a%20crew%20with%20preservation%20experience%20renovated%20the%201%2C400-square-foot%20space.%20The%20process%20took%20seven%20months%20and%20cost%20about%20%24200%2C000.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20wanted%20people%20to%20lose%20track%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20in%20a%20church%2C%20but%20I%20also%20still%20wanted%20them%20to%20feel%20cozy%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHeavenly%20Hideaway%20retained%20many%20of%20the%20church's%20original%20features%2C%20including%20the%20hardwood%20floors.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bartlett%20church%20in%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8de3290413ab8e1d679dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeavenly%20Hideaway%20living%20room.%20%3Cp%3EErik%20Fossum%2FFossum%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHeavenly%20Hideaway's%20living%20room%20is%20a%20cozy%20space%20adorned%20with%20gray%20decor%20and%20wood%20accents.%20Tucker%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20hardwood%20floors%20are%20original%20to%20the%20church%20despite%20being%20water-damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20Tucker%20and%20her%20team%20found%20a%20workaround.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20the%20wood%20from%20the%20bathroom%20to%20replace%20the%20rotten%20wood%20in%20other%20places%20throughout%20the%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20said.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20piece%20of%20hardwood%20that%20you%20see%20is%20original.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20hand-carved%20columns%20that%20featured%20German%20detailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20gourmet%20kitchen%20used%20to%20be%20the%20church's%20sanctuary.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bartlett%20church%20in%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8de846080194819f9cd02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeavenly%20Hideaway%20kitchen.%20%3Cp%3EErik%20Fossum%2FFossum%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHeavenly%20Hideaway%20has%20an%20open-floor%20concept%20that%20connects%2