mmary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20has%20defeated%20Nikki%20Haley%20in%20the%20South%20Carolina%20Republican%20primary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdonald-trump-wins-south-carolina-state-primary-nbc-news-projects-13080350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdonald-trump-wins-south-carolina-state-primary-nbc-news-projects-13080350%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdonald-trump-wins-south-carolina-state-primary-nbc-news-projects-13080350%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Group%20Calls%20To%20End%20Suspension%20Of%20Ops%20Agreement%2C%20Days%20Before%20Review%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20global%20alliance%20of%20Manipur's%20Meitei%20community%20has%20called%20for%20scrapping%20a%20controversial%20ceasefire%20with%20over%20two%20dozen%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%20amid%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%20that%20signed%20the%20tripartite%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20with%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Manipur%20government%20in%202008%20have%20been%20hiding%20under%20the%20SoO%20safety%20net%20%26quot%3Bto%20covertly%20act%20against%20India's%20peace%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Meitei%20Alliance%2C%20a%20group%20whose%20members%20are%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisations%20around%20the%20world%20including%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20Europe%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20a%20joint%20monitoring%20group%20(JMG)%20reviews%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20and%20decides%20whether%20to%20end%20or%20renew%20it.%20The%20next%20review%20is%20on%20February%2029.%20Broadly%2C%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20says%20the%20insurgents%20are%20to%20stay%20at%20designated%20camps%20and%20their%20weapons%20kept%20in%20locked%20storage%2C%20to%20be%20monitored%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20in%20March%202023%20announced%20it%20had%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20with%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Army%20(KNA)%2C%20and%20the%20Zomi%20Revolutionary%20Army%20(ZRA).%20However%2C%20only%20the%20JMG%20can%20decide%20on%20such%20matters%2C%20which%20indicates%20the%20state%20government's%20move%20was%20only%20a%20request%20to%20the%20JMG%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20over%20two%20dozen%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%20come%20under%20two%20umbrella%20groups%20-%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organisation%20(KNO)%2C%20and%20the%20United%20People's%20Front%20(UPF).%20These%20two%20representing%20the%20others%20have%20signed%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuspension%20of%20operations%20with%20any%20armed%20group%20is%2C%20technically%20speaking%2C%20to%20restore%20law%20and%20order%20and%20to%20ensure%20security%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20when%20it%20is%20used%20to%20mask%20privatisation%20of%20violence%2C%20it%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20state%20as%20well%20as%20life%20and%20property%20of%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Bimol%20Akoijam%2C%20professor%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University's%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Social%20Systems%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fiuskq16_manipur-churachandpur-violence-_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20Alliance%20also%20published%20a%20booklet%20detailing%20what%20it%20claimed%20were%20instances%20of%20SoO%20agreement%20ground%20rules%20violations%20by%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKuki-Zo%20armed%20groups%20have%20always%20kept%20their%20larger%20long-term%20political%20goal%20of%20carving%20out%20a%20sovereign%20territory%20called%20Zale'n-gam.%20They%20merely%20take%20advantage%20of%20SoO%20to%20systematically%20build%20up%20their%20strength%20to%20achieve%20prioritised%20goals%20achievable%20within%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Meitei%20Alliance%20said%20in%20the%20booklet%20titled%20'Ghost%20of%20Peace%3A%20Why%20Not%20Abrogate%20SoO%20Agreements%20With%20Kuki%20Armed%20Groups%20to%20Prevent%20Destabilisation%20of%20India%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20long%20run%2C%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%20in%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20borderland%20may%20shift%20allegiance%20and%20become%20the%20proxy%20of%20an%20entirely%20different%2C%20globally%20powerful%20expansionist%20force%20to%20become%20a%20perennial%20threat%20to%20India's%20internal%20security%20and%20more%20extensive%20geostrategic%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Meitei%20Alliance%20said%2C%20days%20after%20it%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20to%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20with%20a%20request%20to%20scrap%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Akoijam%2C%20who%20recently%20published%20a%20report%20on%20the%20media's%20shortcomings%20on%20reporting%20the%20Manipur%20issue%2C%20called%20for%20disarming%20all%20armed%20groups%20in%20order%20to%20end%20the%20%26quot%3Bprivatisation%20of%20violence%26quot%3B%20and%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bonly%20the%20State%20has%20monopoly%20on%20the%20legitimate%20use%20of%20physical%20force%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20indicated%20before%20there%20is%20something%20that%20has%20already%20been%20discussed%20among%20scholars%20and%20activists%20that%20the%20privatisation%20of%20violence%20is%20unacceptable.%20Only%20the%20State%20must%20have%20the%20monopoly%20on%20the%20legitimate%20use%20of%20physical%20force.%20That%20is%20what%20the%20State%20is.%20Now%2C%20if%20you%20privatise%20it%20(violence)%2C%20that%20is%20not%20done...%20Has%20SoO%20become%20something%20like%20a%20mask%20to%20hide%20the%20truth%3F%20That%20is%20something%20people%20have%20to%20ask%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Akoijam%20told%20reporters%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Amend%2C%20Review%20SoO%20Agreement%2C%20Not%20Scrap%20It'%3A%20Retired%20Army%20Officer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Md%20Ali%20Shah%20(retired)%2C%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20panel%20discussion%20on%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday%2C%20recommended%20not%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20scrap%20the%20agreement%2C%20and%20instead%20push%20for%20reviewing%20it%20and%20taking%20corrective%20actions%20to%20ensure%20the%20ground%20rules%20are%20followed%20by%20the%20insurgent%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0kk0k1j_manipur-soo-agreement-event_625x300_24_February_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20slightly%20different%20point%20of%20view.%20I%20am%20sure%20you%20have%20the%20maturity%20to%20understand%20it...%20The%20moment%20any%20agreement%20is%20retracted%2C%20it%20won't%20go%20down%20well.%20I%20personally%20don't%20stand%20for%20termination%20of%20SoO.%20There%20can%20be%20a%20review%2C%20no%20doubt.%20There%20can%20be%20amendments%2C%20no%20doubt.%20But%20terminating%20the%20agreement%20won't%20be%20the%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Major%20Shah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20army%20officer%2C%20Lieutenant%20General%20Konsam%20Himalay%20Singh%20(retired)%2C%20also%20pointed%20at%20the%20scope%20of%20improvement%20of%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%20%26quot%3B...%20Simply%20following%20the%20ground%20rules%20would%20have%20prevented%20the%20worsening%20of%20the%20present%20situation.%20The%20rules%20were%20violated%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20though%20only%20the%20Manipur%20government's%20records%20can%20confirm%20this.%20Even%20now%2C%20there%20is%20scope%20for%20improvement%2C%20like%20biometric%20identification%20of%20the%20inmates%2C%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20camps%2C%20and%20strict%20enforcement%20of%20ground%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20Lt%20General%20Singh%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20violence%20has%20spread%20much%20further.%20Now%20immediate%20and%20forceful%20actions%20to%20contain%20it%20are%20necessary%2C%20including%20all%20illegal%20armed%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lt%20General%20Singh%2C%20the%20first%20officer%20from%20the%20northeast%20to%20become%20a%20Lieutenant%20General%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20and%20who%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Yudh%20Seva%20Medal%20after%20the%20Kargil%20War%20in%201999%2C%20when%20he%20commanded%20the%2027th%20Battalion%2C%20Rajput%20Regiment%2C%20in%20the%20high-altitude%20battlefield%20Siachen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20Against%20Meitei%20Insurgents%20Who%20Signed%20Peace%20Deal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20over%20disagreements%20on%20land%2C%20resources%2C%20political%20representation%2C%20and%20affirmative%20action%20policies%20has%20dragged%20on%20for%20nine%20months%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20accuse%20each%20other%20of%20atrocities.%20The%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20say%20their%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20repelling%20attacks%20by%20armed%20groups%20from%20the%20valley%2C%20who%20come%20to%20the%20hills%20across%20the%20%26quot%3Bbuffer%20zone%26quot%3B%20with%20obvious%20intentions.%20Both%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20definition%20of%20the%20belligerents%20in%20Manipur%20that%20has%20become%20the%20most%20controversial%20since%20nothing%20stops%20these%20%26quot%3Bvolunteers%26quot%3B%20from%20killing%20people%20under%20the%20insurance%20provided%20by%20%26quot%3Bin%20self-defence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F13k1v6cg_moreh_625x300_20_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20members%20of%20Manipur's%20oldest%20valley-based%20armed%20group%20UNLF%2C%20which%20signed%20a%20tripartite%20peace%20agreement%20with%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20in%20November%202023%20-%20the%20first%20Meitei%20insurgent%20group%20to%20do%20so%20-%20are%20allegedly%20engaged%20in%20violent%20activities%20against%20both%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20public%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported%20on%20February%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20sightings%20of%20insurgents%20of%20the%20Kh%20Pambei%20faction%20of%20the%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%20in%20Manipur's%20Moirangpurel%2C%20Tumukhong%2C%20and%20Itham%20have%20raised%20concerns%2C%20with%20reports%20indicating%20they%20were%20carrying%20out%20reconnaissance%20to%20set%20up%20camps%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gates%20of%20houses%20of%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20in%20parts%20of%20Imphal%20valley%20including%20the%20Games%20Village%20in%20the%20Langol%20foothills%20have%20the%20acronym%20'UNLF'%20written%20on%20them%2C%20sources%20who%20have%20been%20to%20the%20area%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20accuse%20the%20Meiteis%20of%20razing%20their%20vacant%20buildings%20and%20occupying%20them%20in%20and%20around%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20have%20pointed%20at%20entire%20localities%20of%20their%20community%20flattened%20and%20erased%20in%20the%20hill%20district%20Churachandpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similarity%20between%20the%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20of%20both%20sides%20is%20that%20they%20appear%20to%20be%20well-armed%20and%20well-equipped%20with%20modern%20battle%20gear.%20The%20security%20forces%20have%20frequently%20recovered%20Russian-origin%20AK%20and%20US-origin%20M%20series%20assault%20rifles%2C%20and%20gun%20models%20commonly%20used%20by%20both%20the%20junta's%20army%20and%20pro-democracy%20insurgents%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20180%20have%20died%20in%20the%20violence%2C%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708797780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Feo44vq28_manipur-soo-agreement-event_625x300_24_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-group-meitei-alliance-calls-to-end-suspension-of-operations-soo-agreement-days-before-review-5120985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20global%20alliance%20of%20Manipur's%20Meitei%20community%20has%20called%20for%20scrapping%20a%20controversial%20ceasefire%20with%20over%20two%20dozen%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%20amid%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-group-meitei-alliance-calls-to-end-suspension-of-operations-soo-agreement-days-before-review-5120985%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-group-meitei-alliance-calls-to-end-suspension-of-operations-soo-agreement-days-before-review-5120985%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-group-meitei-alliance-calls-to-end-suspension-of-operations-soo-agreement-days-before-review-5120985%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20On%20Gujarat%20Visit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Holds%20Mega%20Roadshow%20In%20Jamnagar%22%2C%22cont