%20his%20mother%2C%20more%20than%20a%20week%20after%20he%20died%20in%20an%20Arctic%20prison%20colony%2C%20his%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%2C%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20most%20vocal%20critic%2C%20died%20on%20February%2016%20in%20one%20of%20Russia's%20toughest%20prisons%20in%20northern%20Siberia%2C%20where%20he%20was%20serving%20a%2019-year%20sentence%20on%20charges%20widely%20seen%20as%20political%20retribution%20for%20his%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlexei's%20body%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20his%20mother.%20Many%20thanks%20to%20all%20those%20who%20demanded%20this%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Navalny%20spokesperson%20Kira%20Yarmysh%20said%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAlexey's%20body%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20his%20mother.%20Many%20thanks%20to%20all%20those%20who%20demanded%20this%20with%20us.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLyudmila%20Ivanovna%20is%20still%20in%20Salekhard.%20The%20funeral%20is%20still%20pending.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20if%20the%20authorities%20will%20interfere%20to%20carry%20it%20out%20as%20the%20family%20wants%20and%20as%20Alexey%20deserves.%20We%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20%D0%9A%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%B0%20%D0%AF%D1%80%D0%BC%D1%8B%D1%88%20(%40Kira_Yarmysh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKira_Yarmysh%2Fstatus%2F1761414474643165346%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20week%2C%20Russian%20authorities%20had%20refused%20to%20give%20Lyudmila%20Navalnaya%20custody%20of%20her%20son's%20body%2C%20after%20she%20travelled%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Salekhard%20in%20the%20Yamalo-Nenets%20region%2C%20the%20nearest%20settlement%20to%20the%20prison%20colony%20where%20Navalny%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20team%20on%20Friday%20said%20they%20had%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20to%20obtain%20the%20body%2C%20alleging%20that%20local%20investigators%20had%20threatened%20to%20bury%20him%20on%20the%20prison%20grounds%20if%20his%20mother%20did%20not%20agree%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecret%26quot%3B%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYarmysh%20said%20plans%20for%20the%20funeral%20were%20still%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLyudmila%20Ivanovna%20is%20still%20in%20Salekhard.%20The%20funeral%20is%20still%20pending.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20if%20the%20authorities%20will%20interfere%20to%20carry%20it%20out%20as%20the%20family%20wants%20and%20as%20Alexei%20deserves%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20team%20said%20previously%20the%20Kremlin%20was%20trying%20to%20block%20a%20public%20funeral%2C%20which%20could%20turn%20into%20a%20show%20of%20support%20for%20Navalny's%20movement%20and%20his%20opposition%20to%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20leader%2C%20who%20famously%20never%20said%20Navalny's%20name%20in%20public%2C%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20death%20of%20his%20most%20vocal%20critic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20spokesman%2C%20Dmitry%20Peskov%2C%20has%20criticised%20statements%20by%20Navalny's%20wife%20and%20Western%20leaders%20that%20blamed%20Putin%20for%20his%20death%20as%20%26quot%3Bvulgar%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Satanism'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20authorities%20said%20Navalny%20died%20of%20%26quot%3Bnatural%20causes%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20lost%20consciousness%20following%20a%20walk%20in%20the%20prison%20colony%2C%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BPolar%20Wolf%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20team%20said%20investigators%20were%20holding%20on%20to%20his%20body%2C%20refusing%20for%20days%20to%20let%20his%20mother%20even%20see%20it%20--%20prompting%20accusations%20the%20state%20were%20%26quot%3Bkillers%26quot%3B%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bcover%20their%20tracks%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Russians%20signed%20a%20petition%20callin