%20education%20department%20claimed%20the%20suspension%20order%20was%20issued%20after%20an%20initial%20inquiry%20into%20hurting%20and%20provoking%20religious%20sentiments%20against%20the%20teacher%20was%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20initial%20inquiry%20into%20the%20controversy%20over%20placing%20Goddess%20Saraswati's%20picture%20on%20stage%20at%20a%20Republic%20Day%20function%20in%20the%20government%20primary%20school%20at%20Lakadia%20in%20Kishanganj%20area%2C%20the%20teacher%20was%20found%20responsible%20for%20hurting%20and%20provoking%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20local%20people%20and%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20that%2C%20order%20for%20her%20suspension%20was%20issued%20on%20Friday%2C%20Baran%20district%20education%20(elementary)%20officer%20Piyush%20Kumar%20Sharma%20told%20PTI%20on%20Saturday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20added%20the%20teacher%20was%20also%20ordered%20to%20register%20her%20attendance%20at%20the%20directorate%2C%20elementary%20education%2C%20Bikaner%2C%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher%20could%20have%20averted%20the%20controversy%20and%20allowed%20the%20Republic%20Day%20function%20to%20go%20on%20smoothly%2C%20simply%20by%20agreeing%20with%20the%20locals%20and%20placing%20Goddess%20Saraswati's%20picture%2C%20but%20instead%20she%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20and%20provoked%20the%20locals%2C%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dispute%20had%20erupted%20between%20the%20primary%20teacher%20and%20other%20villagers%20during%20the%20Republic%20Day%20function%20in%20the%20school%20on%20January%2026%20this%20year.%20Ms%20Bairwa%20refused%20to%20put%20the%20picture%20of%20Goddess%20Saraswati%20on%20stage%20at%20the%20function%20along%20with%20photos%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Bhim%20Rao%20Ambedkar%20despite%20local%20villagers%20insisting%20that%20it%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher%20further%20provoked%20the%20locals%20saying%20Goddess%20Saraswati%20contributed%20nothing%20to%20