%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Eiffel%20Tower%20strike%20ended%2C%20and%20the%20site%20will%20reopen%20on%20Sunday.%20SETE%20and%20trade%20unions%20agreed%20to%20regularly%20review%20the%20business%20model%2C%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20and%20sales.%20Refunds%20will%20be%20given%20to%20those%20who%20purchased%20tickets%20between%20February%2019%20and%2024.%20The%20winners'%20medals%20at%20the%202024%20Summer%20Olympics%20will%20contain%20metal%20from%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feiffel-tower-strike-ends-site-to-reopen-on-sunday%2Farticleshow%2F107972546.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feiffel-tower-strike-ends-site-to-reopen-on-sunday%2Famp_articleshow%2F107972546.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feiffel-tower-strike-ends-site-to-reopen-on-sunday%2Famp_articleshow%2F107972546.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Russia's%20Military%20Uses%20Volunteer%20Fighters%20To%20Plug%20Gaps%20In%20Ukraine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Russian%20forces%20withdrew%20from%20the%20town%20of%20Balakliia%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20in%20late%202022%2C%20pursued%20by%20Ukrainian%20troops%20and%20under%20artillery%20fire%2C%20they%20left%20a%20poorly%20equipped%20group%20of%20volunteers%20to%20guard%20their%20retreat.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20force%20of%20around%2050%20men%20came%20from%20the%20%E2%80%AFNational%20Army%20Combat%20Reserve%20-%20known%20by%20its%20Russian%20acronym%20BARS%20-%20a%20loose%20assembly%20of%20units%20totaling%20several%20thousand%20fighters%20that%20Russia's%20defense%20ministry%20has%20deployed%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20supplement%20its%20regular%20forces.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20four%20hours%20of%20footage%20from%20a%20bodycam%20worn%20by%20one%20of%20the%20fighters%2C%20obtained%20by%20Reuters%2C%20provides%20a%20rare%20first-hand%20view%20of%20the%20combat%20operations%20of%20a%20BARS%20unit%2C%20according%20to%20three%20military%20experts%20who%20reviewed%20the%20video%20to%20provide%20an%20assessment%20for%20the%20news%20agency%20of%20the%20unit's%20military%20capability.%E2%80%AF%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20marked%20the%20first%20time%20BARS%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202015%2C%20deployed%20units%20in%20combat.%20The%20video%2C%20coupled%20with%20interviews%20with%20four%20platoon%20members%2C%20shows%20the%20BARS%20unit%20was%20left%20to%20defend%20Balakliia%20with%20no%20heavy%20weaponry%20or%20air%20support%2C%20malfunctioning%20communications%2C%20and%20confused%20coordination%20with%20the%20regular%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20is%20our%20air%20force%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20one%20of%20the%20BARS%20fighters.%E2%80%AF%20His%20squad%2C%20tasked%20with%20defending%20a%20crossroads%20north%20of%20the%20town%2C%20was%20sharing%20a%20mess%20tin%20of%20cold%20meat%20stew%20during%20a%20break%20in%20Ukrainian%20shelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20squad%20leader%2C%20Anton%20Kuznetsov%2C%20whose%20bodycam%20recorded%20the%20exchange%2C%20told%20the%20men%20that%20there%20must%20be%20a%20good%20reason%20there%20was%20no%20air%20support.%20%26quot%3BDo%20they%20understand%20that%20we're%20surrounded%3F%26quot%3B%20complained%20another%20soldier%2C%20off-camera.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContacted%20by%20Reuters%2C%20Kuznetsov%20said%20that%20he%20had%20made%20the%20bodycam%20video%20and%20had%20then%20misplaced%20the%20camera's%20memory%20card%20but%20he%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20combat%20operations.%20The%20memory%20card%20was%20left%20behind%20in%20a%20rucksack%20after%20the%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20defence%20ministry%20and%20the%20Kremlin%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20about%20the%20video%20or%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20military%20relies%20on%20the%20BARS%20irregulars.%20A%20deputy%20commander%20of%20the%20BARS%209%20force%20that%20fought%20in%20Balakliia%2C%20contacted%20by%20Reuters%2C%20confirmed%20his%20position%20in%20the%20unit%20but%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20its%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20could%20not%20independently%20determine%20how%20representative%20the%20conditions%20in%20the%20video%20were%20of%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20wider%20BARS%20force.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20made%20territorial%20gains%20along%20parts%20of%20the%20frontline%20in%20recent%20months.%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20replaced%20its%20military%20top%20brass%20in%20early%20February%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20it%20needs%20more%20equipment%20and%20support%20from%20Western%20allies%20to%20prosecute%20the%20war.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20at%20least%20two%20occasions%2C%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20publicly%20praised%20the%20contribution%20of%20BARS%20to%20Russia's%20campaign.%20In%20a%20Feb.%2021%2C%202023%20annual%20address%20to%20parliament%2C%20he%20said%20BARS%20fighters%20were%20patriotic%20volunteers%20and%20thanked%20them%20for%20their%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20war%20enters%20a%20third%20year%2C%20BARS%20is%20part%20of%20a%20patchwork%20of%20irregular%20forces%20that%20helps%20Russia%20avoid%20an%20unpopular%20general%20draft%2C%20the%20military%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERod%20Thornton%2C%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20Defence%20Studies%20Department%20of%20King's%20College%20London%2C%20estimated%20that%20BARS%20contributes%E2%80%AF%20between%2010%2C000%20and%2030%2C000%20men%20to%20a%20Russian%20force%20operating%20in%20or%20near%20Ukraine%20of%20about%20200%2C000.%E2%80%AF%20Russia%20does%20not%E2%80%AF%20disclose%20the%20number%20of%20BARS%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20BARS%20units%20have%20been%20fighting%20in%20north-east%20Ukraine%20and%20in%20the%20southern%20Zaporizhzhia%20region%2C%20two%20of%20the%20most%20bitterly%20contested%20fronts%2C%20according%20to%20updates%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20by%20Dmitry%20Rogozin%2C%20the%20Moscow-appointed%20representative%20for%20Zaporizhzhia%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20of%20the%20Russian%20parliament%2C%20and%20a%20report%20from%20Russian%20state%20news%20agency%20RIA%20Novosti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBARS%20units%20were%20useful%20in%20plugging%20gaps%20in%20Russian%20manpower%2C%20said%20Nick%20Reynolds%2C%20Research%20Fellow%20in%20Land%20Warfare%20at%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20(RUSI)%2C%20a%20UK-based%20defence%20think%20tank.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20Russian%20state%20clearly%20mobilizing%20for%20a%20longer%20conflict%2C%20a%20system%20such%20as%20BARS%20does%20provide%20an%20additional%20avenue%20from%20which%20to%20mobilize%20parts%20of%20the%20population%2C%20get%20them%20trained%20and%20provide%20additional%20mass%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reynolds%2C%20who%20reviewed%20the%20bodycam%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20group%20shown%20in%20the%20video%20appeared%20%26quot%3Bnot%20particularly%20professional%20or%20well%20trained.%26quot%3B%E2%80%AF%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%AF%26quot%3BWE'D%20BEEN%20FORGOTTEN%26quot%3B%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sept.%206%2C%202022%2C%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Russian%20force%20in%20Balakliia%20was%20withdrawing%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20major%20Ukrainian%20counter-offensive.%20Ukrainian%20forces%20have%20already%20taken%20the%20nearby%20settlements%20of%20Verbivka%20and%20Lagery.%20But%20the%20BARS%20fighters%20stayed%20behind.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuznetsov%2C%20aged%2029%20and%20from%20Siberia%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20squad%20leaders%20of%20a%20BARS%209%20platoon%2C%20in%20command%20of%20around%20a%20dozen%20men%2C%20the%20video%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commander%20of%20the%20BARS%20platoon%20inside%20Balakliia%20ordered%20Kuznetsov's%20squad%20to%20head%20to%20the%20crossroads%20and%20repel%20Ukrainian%20forces%2C%20the%20video%20showed.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20knew%20they%20would%20be%20outgunned%20by%20the%20Ukrainians%2C%20conversations%20caught%20on%20camera%20showed.%20The%20heaviest%20weapons%20Kuznetsov's%20squad%20had%20at%20its%20disposal%20were%20machine%20guns%2C%20rocket-propelled%20grenades%2C%20and%20mortars.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20members%20of%20the%20BARS%20force%20were%20sent%20to%20find%20a%20spot%20with%20radio%20signal%20to%20contact%20a%20nearby%20artillery%20unit%20to%20get%20support%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20four%20fighters%20who%20spoke%20to%20Reuters%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20around%2024%20hours%2C%20they%20located%20an%20artillery%20unit%2C%20but%20they%20were%20already%20pulling%20back%20towards%20Russia%2C%20so%20could%20not%20help%2C%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20first%20impression%20was%20that%20we'd%20been%20forgotten%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20hit%20me%20very%20hard%20psychologically.%26quot%3B%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETOY%20SOLDIERS%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sept%207%2C%E2%80%AFthe%20last%20day%20recorded%20on%20the%20bodycam%2C%20Kuznetsov's%20squad%20were%20keeping%20watch%20from%20an%20apartment%20building%20overlooking%20the%20crossroads%2C%20as%20radio%20traffic%20reported%20Ukrainian%20forces%20approaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20waited%2C%20Kuznetsov%20and%20two%20of%20his%20men%20played%20with%20a%20toy%20plane%20and%20toy%20tank%2C%20pantomiming%20a%20soldier%20requesting%20air%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20a%20radio%20report%20came%20in%20saying%20five%20Ukrainian%20Humvees%20were%20spotted%20nearby.%20Kuznetsov%20tells%20his%20squad%3A%20%26quot%3BRight%2C%20men%2C%20let's%20get%20into%20the%20mood%20for%20a%20battle.%26quot%3B%E2%80%AF%20The%20video%20footage%20ends%20as%20Kuznetsov%20heads%20downstairs%20into%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20fighters%20told%20Reuters%20they%20did%20engage%20the%20Ukrainian%20forces%2C%20but%20the%20Russians%20were%20outnumbered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20retreat%2C%20BARS%209%20temporarily%20disbanded%2C%20according%20to%20the%20same%20two%20fighters%2C%20though%20they%20said%20it%20has%20since%20been%20re-started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708791300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F1opep18o_russia-bars-force-reuters_625x300_24_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraine-russia-war-how-russias-military-uses-volunteer-fighters-to-plug-gaps-in-ukraine-5119106%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Russian%20forces%20withdrew%20from%20the%20town%20of%20Balakliia%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20in%20late%202022%2C%20pursued%20by%20Ukrainian%20troops%20and%20under%20artillery%20fire%2C%20they%20left%20a%20poorly%20equipped%20group%20of%20volunteers%20to%20guard%20their%20retreat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraine-russia-war-how-russias-military-uses-volunteer-fighters-to-plug-gaps-in-ukraine-5119106%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraine-russia-war-how-russias-military-uses-volunteer-fighters-to-plug-gaps-in-ukraine-5119106%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraine-russia-war-how-russias-military-uses-volunteer-fighters-to-plug-gaps-in-ukraine-5119106%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Navalny's%20body%20handed%20over%20to%20his%20mother%20week%20after%2