etter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GettyImages%201140985597%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d9fba190413ab8e1d6a503%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWarren%20Buffett%2C%20CEO%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20and%20former%20vice%20chairman%20Charlie%20Munger.%3Cp%3EJOHANNES%20EISELE%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWarren%20Buffett%20hailed%20Charlie%20Munger%20as%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3Barchitect%26quot%3B%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20in%20his%20annual%20letter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20investor%20also%20called%20out%20stock-market%20gamblers%20who%20buy%C2%A0%26quot%3Bhot%20stocks%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blottery%20tickets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBuffett%20dismissed%20forecasters%2C%20warned%20Berkshire's%20scale%20is%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20nodded%20to%20the%20AI%20frenzy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWarren%20Buffett%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Charlie%20Munger%2C%20touted%20four%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20biggest%20bets%2C%20and%20voiced%20frustration%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fberkshirehathaway.com%2Fletters%2F2023ltr.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20letter%20to%20shareholders%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20famed%20investor%20and%20Berkshire%20CEO%20also%20called%20out%20stock-market%20gamblers%20and%20speculators%2C%20dismissed%20Wall%20Street%20forecasters%2C%20and%20even%20nodded%20to%20the%20AI%20craze%20while%20championing%20his%20hometown%20of%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMunger%2C%20Buffett's%20business%20partner%20and%20Berkshire's%20vice%20chairman%20for%20over%20four%20decades%2C%20died%20in%20November%20at%2099.%20He%20shaped%20Berkshire%20into%20a%20world-beating%20conglomerate%20and%20helped%20Buffett%20evolve%20from%20bargain%20hunting%20to%20buying%20businesses%20at%20fair%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20I%20have%20long%20been%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20construction%20crew%3B%20Charlie%20should%20forever%20be%20credited%20with%20being%20the%20architect%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20said%20in%20his%20letter%2C%20describing%20himself%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgeneral%20contractor%26quot%3B%20who%20realized%20Munger's%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEchoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-annual-shareholder-letter-coke-amex-buybacks-taxes-earnings-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elast%20year's%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20centibillionaire%20hailed%20Berkshire's%20large%20stakes%20in%20Coca-Cola%20and%20American%20Express%2C%20which%20it%20hasn't%20touched%20in%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20as%20emblematic%20of%20his%20company's%20long-term%20investing%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20also%20praised%20Occidental%20Petroleum%2C%20which%20he's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-oxy-stock-portfolio-crownrock-oil-price-berkshire-wti-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilt%20a%20nearly%2028%25%20stake%20in%20from%20scratch%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20He%20trumpeted%20the%20oil-and-gas%20explorer%20and%20producer%20for%20supporting%20US%20energy%20independence%20and%20pioneering%20carbon-capture%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shouted%20out%20Berkshire's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-japan-trading-houses-inflation-recession-economy-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroughly%209%25%20stakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20five%20Japanese%20trading%20houses%2C%20which%20he%20started%20amassing%20back%20in%20July%202019.%20He%20celebrated%20their%20restraint%20in%20compensating%20executives%2C%20their%20discipline%20in%20paying%20dividends%2C%20and%20their%20long-term%2C%20conservative%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20seemed%20resigned%2C%20however%2C%20that%20Berkshire%20has%20grown%20so%20big%20that%20there%20are%20few%20other%20directions%20for%20it%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stockpicker%20explained%20that%20Berkshire%20is%20now%20so%20large%20%E2%80%94%20it%20had%20%24561%20billion%20of%20net%20assets%20at%20the%20end%20of%20December%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20American%20company%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it's%20extremely%20hard%20to%20make%20purchases%20that%20are%20big%20enough%20to%20materially%20accelerate%20its%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20remain%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20companies%20in%20this%20country%20capable%20of%20truly%20moving%20the%20needle%20at%20Berkshire%2C%20and%20they%20have%20been%20endlessly%20picked%20over%20by%20us%20and%20by%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20there%20are%20virtually%20none%20outside%20the%20United%20States%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20in%20all%2C%20we%20have%20no%20possibility%20of%20eye-popping%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20also%20criticized%20speculators%20in%20his%20letter%2C%20noting%20that%20stock%20traders%20are%20%26quot%3Bneither%20more%20emotionally%20stable%20nor%20better%20taught%26quot%3B%20than%20when%20he%20was%20a%20student.%20He%20also%20noted%20the%20proliferation%20of%20stock-trading%20apps%20has%20made%20daily%20buying%20and%20selling%20easier%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarkets%20now%20exhibit%20far%20more%20casino-like%20behavior%20than%20they%20did%20when%20I%20was%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20casino%20now%20resides%20in%20many%20homes%20and%20daily%20tempts%20the%20occupants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20same%20lines%2C%20Buffett%20said%20that%20he%20imagines%20Berkshire%20shareholders%20to%20be%20long-term%20holders%2C%20not%20people%20who%20use%20their%20spare%20cash%20to%20%26quot%3Bpurchase%20lottery%20tickets%20or%20'hot%20stocks.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20also%20brushed%20off%20the%20army%20of%20experts%20predicting%20market%20crashes%20and%20recessions%20or%20giving%20stock%20tips%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPundits%20should%20always%20be%20ignored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20questioning%20why%20they%20would%20share%20their%20forecasts%20if%20they%20were%20certain%20they'd%20come%20true.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20like%20finding%20gold%20and%20then%20handing%20a%20map%20to%20the%20neighbors%20showing%20its%20location.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20also%20remarked%20that%20Omaha%20has%20produced%20himself%20and%20Munger%3B%20the%20heads%20of%20Berkshire's%20insurance%20and%20non-insurance%20divisions%2C%20Ajit%20Jain%20and%20Greg%20Abel%3B%20and%20his%20sister%2C%20Bertie%2C%20who%20he%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20country's%20great%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20what%20is%20going%20on%3F%20Is%20it%20Omaha's%20water%3F%20Is%20it%20Omaha's%20air%3F%20Is%20it%20some%20strange%20planetary%20phenomenon%20akin%20to%20that%20which%20has%20produced%20Jamaica's%20sprinters%2C%20Kenya's%20marathon%20runners%2C%20or%20Russia's%20chess%20experts%3F%20Must%20we%20wait%20until%20AI%20someday%20yields%20the%20answer%20to%20this%20puzzle%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-letter-munger-berkshire-annual-shareholder-stock-speculation-ai-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708786298000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d9fbdd90413ab8e1d6a50a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-letter-munger-berkshire-annual-shareholder-stock-speculation-ai-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett's%20annual%20letter%20slammed%20speculators%20who%20buy%20%26quot%3Bhot%20stocks%26quot%3B%20like%20%26quot%3Blottery%20tickets.