20Bhagwad%20Gita%20and%20the%20Ramayana.%20She%20was%20well-versed%20in%20Sanskrit%20and%20was%20a%20fan%20of%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20and%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20surprised%20to%20know%20she%20had%20never%20been%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Daman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20has%20goodwill%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20kindness%20never%20left%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Daman%20recounts%20how%20a%20man%20named%20Anil%20helped%20him%20through%20a%20sticky%20spot.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20car%20had%20broken%20down%20and%20it%20was%20very%20expensive%20to%20hire%20a%20pickup%20truck%20there.%20I%20had%20visited%20Anil%20for%20a%20few%20car-related%20things%20the%20previous%20day%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20car%20broke%20down%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20could%20send%20someone%20to%20help.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20Anil%20drive%20600%20miles%20to%20help%20but%20did%20not%20charge%20a%20penny%20for%20it.%20%E2%80%9CYesterday%20when%20you%20drove%20Lal%20Pari%20to%20my%20garage%2C%20you%20brought%20a%20smile%20to%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20face.%20I%20cannot%20charge%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20was%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20excuse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%E2%80%99s%20more%20fascinating%20is%20the%20number%20of%20people%20Daman%20met%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334987%2Fmumbai-battling-rheumatoid-arthritis-parvinder-chawla-shares-tips-on-wheelchair-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20incredible%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20undertook%20%E2%80%93%20fifty%20thousand%20people%20and%20counting!%20And%20when%20he%20finally%20reached%20the%20destination%2C%20the%20exhilaration%20was%20visible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cim