20support%20students%20throughout%20their%20entire%20admissions%20journey.%20Our%20ultimate%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20a%20comprehensive%20global%20AI%20admissions%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CRegardless%20of%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20background%20or%20location%2C%20our%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20equal%20opportunities%20and%20access%20to%20the%20right%20guidance%2C%20a%20privilege%20often%20reserved%20for%20the%20affluent%20or%20those%20able%20to%20afford%20expensive%20counsellors.%20We%20leverage%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126973%2Fkerala-police-equips-personnel-cutting-edge-body-cameras%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20technology%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20AI%2C%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20AI%20comes%20into%20play%20with%20the%20process%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20employ%20AI%20in%20two%20primary%20areas.%20Firstly%2C%20we%20utilise%20it%20to%20assist%20students%20in%20determining%20the%20most%20suitable%20program%20or%20university%20currently%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20there%20are%20existing%20filtration%20tools%20enabling%20students%20to%20filter%20courses%20they%20are%20eligible%20for%20and%20view%20them%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20an%20additional%20step%20forward.%20We%20incorporate%20preferences%20into%20the%20equation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20AI%20strives%20to%20understand%20and%20integrate%20the%20individual%20preferences%20of%20each%20student%20into%20the%20recommendations%20that%20it%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20accomplish%20this%20through%20our%20proprietary%20recommendation%20engine%2C%20which%20has%20been%20trained%20on%20over%2015%20million%20acceptance%20and%20admit%20data%20points.%20While%20it%E2%80%99s%20certainly%20possible%20for%20students%20to%20conduct%20this%20research%20themselves%20by%20visiting%20numerous%20websites%2C%20reading%20various%20articles%2C%20and%20compiling%20the%20information%20manually%2C%20our%20platform%20streamlines%20this%20process%20significantly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20synthesising%20and%20analysing%20vast%20amounts%20of%20information%2C%20the%20platform%20can%20deliver%20personalised%20recommendations%20quickly%20and%20seamlessly%2C%20saving%20students%20valuable%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20where%20AI%20comes%20in%20to%20help%20the%20students%20is%20writing%20their%20personal%20essays.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20students%20know%20what%20college%20they%20want%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20to%20write%20a%20stellar%20essay.%20We%20trained%20our%20model%20with%205%2C000%20accepted%20essays%20from%20across%20universities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20begin%20by%20ensuring%20basic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341068%2Fteach-spoken-english-on-youtube-dehati-madam-uttar-pradesh-yashoda-lodhi-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrammar%20and%20punctuation%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20correct.%20Beyond%20these%20fundamentals%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20delivery%20and%20specificity.%20Delivery%20pertains%20to%20how%20effectively%20the%20essay%20is%20conveyed%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20while%20specificity%20refers%20to%20its%20relevance%20to%20the%20programme%20being%20applied%20for%20and%20the%20individual%20applicant%E2%80%99s%20profile.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%